      Subclasses of WeatherObserver in <Unnamed> 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ForecastApp
      A weather forecast app determines if the pressure readings from its subscribed weather station, if any, indicate it is likely to rain due to a reduction on the pressure level.
      class  StatisticsApp
      A weather statistics app calculates the minimum, maximum, and average temperature read so far from its subscribed weather station, if any.
